## Template Customization Guide

**To use this template:**

1. Replace `[Feature Name]` in title
2. Update status badge (✅ Complete, ⚠️ Partial, 📋 Planned)
3. Fill in TL;DR with 2-3 sentences
4. List 3-5 key files with actual paths
5. Customize pre-flight checklist (4-6 items each)
6. Write overview (2-3 paragraphs)
7. Add How It Works with code examples
8. Add validation commands (3-5 concrete tests)
9. Document 3-5 common mistakes
10. Delete this customization guide section

**Minimum viable feature doc**:
- Title + Status
- TL;DR
- Key Files (3 files minimum)
- Pre-flight Checklist

**Can expand later**:
- Performance section
- Migration guide
- Advanced examples

**See `ADAPTATION-GUIDE.md` for detailed instructions**
